version_description: This version uses capo on the 2nd fret. Easier to play.
Includes B7 instead of B and A-G walkdown in verses.
I've written out tabs for the Pre-Chorus.
Em changed to E. It is more accurate.
Added Chorus Riff, Added Strumming Pattern, Changed the Song to Power Chords.

song_name: A Rush Of Blood To The Head
